3
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,625
[REITA] 
"To Mr. Kusuo Saiki.

4
00:01:43,708 --> 00:01:46,375
"I am someone who knows you have
psychic powers, but don't worry.

5
00:01:46,458 --> 00:01:48,458
"I intend to tell
no one about you.

6
00:01:48,541 --> 00:01:50,166
"I'm writing this letter

7
00:01:50,250 --> 00:01:52,000
"because I wanted to tell you
that I'm not your enemy,

8
00:01:52,083 --> 00:01:53,750
"and that I want to be
your apprentice.

9
00:01:53,833 --> 00:01:56,333
"To tell you the truth,
I also have unique abilities.

10
00:01:56,416 --> 00:01:57,750
"It is because of
those abilities

11
00:01:57,833 --> 00:01:59,416
that I came to know
about you, master."

12
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:01,125
[SAIKI] He's all ready
calling me master?

13
00:02:01,208 --> 00:02:02,958
[REITA] "I'll come to greet
you in person sometime soon.

14
00:02:03,041 --> 00:02:04,333
Sincerely,
Your Faithful Servant."

15
00:02:04,416 --> 00:02:06,541
[SAIKI] He's gone from
apprentice to servant.

16
00:02:06,625 --> 00:02:09,250
But the real news is there's
another psychic out there.

17
00:02:09,333 --> 00:02:10,875
Wonder what he's like.

18
00:02:10,958 --> 00:02:13,458
I should find out
before he shows up.

19
00:02:13,541 --> 00:02:15,958
Psychometry--

20
00:02:16,041 --> 00:02:18,666
the ability to read
a person's feelings and memories

21
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:20,250
that have been stored in
an inanimate object,

22
00:02:20,333 --> 00:02:23,250
like, for example,
this <i>Shonen Jump.</i>

23
00:02:23,333 --> 00:02:27,125
The printing process.
Major story spoilers.

24
00:02:27,208 --> 00:02:28,791
Overworked writers.

25
00:02:28,875 --> 00:02:30,750
Just touching it,
I'm overwhelmed with all this,

26
00:02:30,833 --> 00:02:32,125
which is why I always wear

27
00:02:32,208 --> 00:02:33,708
extremely thin
transparent gloves

28
00:02:33,791 --> 00:02:36,958
that help to keep
this power in check.

29
00:02:37,041 --> 00:02:39,916
My psychometry only works
when I touch things directly,

30
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,666
but now the gloves are off,
so I can see what this guy is--

31
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:43,958
[doorbell rings]

32
00:02:44,041 --> 00:02:46,458
Wow, your house
is really normal.

33
00:02:46,541 --> 00:02:49,166
This is too soon. Why
even bother sending a letter?

34
00:02:49,250 --> 00:02:51,208
Ah, sorry.
Where are my manners?

35
00:02:51,291 --> 00:02:52,666
My name's Reita Toritsuka,

36
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:54,583
and it's a pleasure
to meet you, master.

37
00:02:54,666 --> 00:02:56,500
Let's see, I'm 16 years old--

38
00:02:56,583 --> 00:02:58,416
Ah, but you know all that
'cause you can read my mind.

39
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:00,250
Anyway, feels like I know you.

40
00:03:00,333 --> 00:03:02,208
I've heard so much about you
from people. From dead people.

41
00:03:02,291 --> 00:03:03,833
Did I forget to mention
that part?

42
00:03:03,916 --> 00:03:05,208
[SAIKI] That explains it.
He's a medium.

43
00:03:05,291 --> 00:03:07,083
You can't see spirits, master?

44
00:03:07,166 --> 00:03:08,916
Not unless you're one.

45
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:11,250
Oh, good for you.
I see about 15 right now.

46
00:03:11,333 --> 00:03:14,458
Really? That sounds like a lot.
What, are they having a party?

47
00:03:14,541 --> 00:03:17,416
Nothing draws a crowd of spirits
like a psychic. They're curious.

48
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:20,250
There's an old lady hanging out
up in that corner there.

49
00:03:20,333 --> 00:03:22,333
And right next to you is a guy
bouncing his bare butt.

50
00:03:22,416 --> 00:03:24,041
But forget about that.

51
00:03:24,125 --> 00:03:25,666
The reason I'm here
is I wanna be your apprentice.

52
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:27,541
Wait. He's doing what
with his butt now?

53
00:03:27,625 --> 00:03:29,458
[REITA] Don't worry.
It's totally harmless.

54
00:03:29,541 --> 00:03:30,625
Harms my peace of mind.

55
00:03:30,708 --> 00:03:32,041
Oh, looks like he's gone now.

56
00:03:32,125 --> 00:03:34,000
Nope. he's rubbing his butt
on his face.

57
00:03:34,083 --> 00:03:35,833
You know I hear your thoughts,
right?

58
00:03:35,916 --> 00:03:37,958
I'm sorry. I don't really have
any control over these guys.

59
00:03:38,041 --> 00:03:40,000
You're a psychic medium.
Can't you just...

60
00:03:40,083 --> 00:03:41,500
Be gone.
or something?

61
00:03:41,583 --> 00:03:43,333
Yeah, well, my abilities
are pretty much limited

62
00:03:43,416 --> 00:03:45,416
to seeing ghosts
and talking to 'em.

63
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:48,583
I've had this gift since birth
when I was born into a temple.

64
00:03:48,666 --> 00:03:50,791
From birth?
We're the same in that manner.

65
00:03:50,875 --> 00:03:52,583
[REITA] When I was little,

66
00:03:52,666 --> 00:03:54,583
I couldn't tell the difference
between people and ghosts.

67
00:03:54,666 --> 00:03:56,166
Then my beloved grandma
told me that spirits

68
00:03:56,250 --> 00:03:57,750
can't take on physical form,

69
00:03:57,833 --> 00:03:59,375
so that's a good way
to identify 'em.

70
00:03:59,458 --> 00:04:01,125
I was so relieved,
I went to give her a hug,

71
00:04:01,208 --> 00:04:04,166
and that's when I discovered
Grandma was a ghost.

72
00:04:04,250 --> 00:04:05,666
[SAIKI] That's dark.

73
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:07,041
[REITA] Yeah,
I was pretty bummed,

74
00:04:07,125 --> 00:04:08,708
but my grandpa came
to cheer me up,

75
00:04:08,791 --> 00:04:10,375
except he was a ghost, too.

76
00:04:10,458 --> 00:04:12,375
After that, I just started
hugging people at random.

77
00:04:12,458 --> 00:04:14,458
A lot of 'em thought
I was being creepy and gross,

78
00:04:14,541 --> 00:04:16,708
but, really, I was just checking
to make sure they were alive.

79
00:04:16,791 --> 00:04:18,583
[SAIKI] That sketchy grin
says otherwise.

80
00:04:18,666 --> 00:04:20,666
When it comes to powers, I drew
the short end of the stick.

81
00:04:20,750 --> 00:04:22,916
It's more of a burden
than a gift with no upside.

82
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,875
That's not true.
By communicating with the dead,

83
00:04:24,958 --> 00:04:27,125
think of all the people
you can bring closure to.

84
00:04:27,208 --> 00:04:29,125
Yeah, but is there any way
I can get rich off of it?

85
00:04:29,208 --> 00:04:31,958
Uh, got you.

86
00:04:32,041 --> 00:04:33,791
When I heard about you
from my ghost friends,

87
00:04:33,875 --> 00:04:35,333
I knew I had to meet you.

88
00:04:35,416 --> 00:04:37,041
He said there was a guy
with all kinds of powers

89
00:04:37,125 --> 00:04:38,750
like telepathy, x-ray vision,

90
00:04:38,833 --> 00:04:41,250
teleportation, clairvoyance,
and psychokinesis.

91
00:04:41,333 --> 00:04:43,625
But you still cared more about
the ladies' bath, didn't you?

92
00:04:43,708 --> 00:04:45,541
Please, Saiki,
make me your apprentice

93
00:04:45,625 --> 00:04:47,333
and teach me how to do all of
your tricks. I'm begging you.

94
00:04:47,416 --> 00:04:49,291
Even if I could teach you
these abilities,

95
00:04:49,375 --> 00:04:51,291
you'd just use 'em
to do gross stuff, right?

96
00:04:51,375 --> 00:04:53,083
Look, I'm not gonna lie to you,

97
00:04:53,166 --> 00:04:54,958
because I respect you and also
because you can read my mind

98
00:04:55,041 --> 00:04:56,916
and would know that I was lying.

99
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,916
To be honest, I mostly want to
see through girls' clothes

100
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,000
and predict lottery numbers.
Tell me, is that so wrong?

101
00:05:01,083 --> 00:05:02,666
That was too honest.

102
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:04,458
I think clairvoyance
could help with peeping, too.

103
00:05:04,541 --> 00:05:06,500
Plus, I want to lift skirts with
psychokinesis and teleport...

104
00:05:06,583 --> 00:05:08,250
Never seen a scumbag
with such pure eyes.

105
00:05:08,333 --> 00:05:10,458
But these powers
don't work how he thinks.

106
00:05:10,541 --> 00:05:12,458
People's voices
flood into your head constantly.

107
00:05:12,541 --> 00:05:13,916
You see through things
too well

108
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,833
and can't touch anything
without gloves on.

109
00:05:15,916 --> 00:05:19,583
You have no idea how hard it is.
Being a psychic is suffering.

110
00:05:19,666 --> 00:05:21,708
Uhh. Guess I should be
going now.

111
00:05:21,791 --> 00:05:23,541
[SAIKI] Don't tell anyone
about this, okay?

112
00:05:23,625 --> 00:05:24,958
But can I come see you again?

113
00:05:25,041 --> 00:05:26,708
Just get out of here all re--

114
00:05:26,791 --> 00:05:29,708
Psychometry? I forgot
to put my glove back on.

115
00:05:29,791 --> 00:05:31,041
When I touch other people,

116
00:05:31,125 --> 00:05:32,708
it's like their senses
become my own.

117
00:05:32,791 --> 00:05:34,500
Uh, master?

118
00:05:34,583 --> 00:05:36,583
[timer dings]

119
00:05:36,666 --> 00:05:38,708
[REITA] Master,
is something wrong?

120
00:05:38,791 --> 00:05:41,875
[SAIKI] Well, I guess
we're both suffering.

121
00:05:41,958 --> 00:05:44,958
♪

122
00:05:46,958 --> 00:05:49,291
[SAIKI] Last night, I had
a surprise drop-in from--

123
00:05:49,375 --> 00:05:51,000
what was his name--
Toritsuka?

124
00:05:51,083 --> 00:05:53,375
You hear about the cool
new transfer student next door?

125
00:05:53,458 --> 00:05:54,541
Really?

126
00:05:54,625 --> 00:05:56,125
♪

127
00:05:56,208 --> 00:05:58,416
Ooh, can you tell me
what my guardian spirit is like?

128
00:05:58,500 --> 00:06:00,041
She looks like
a noblewoman,

129
00:06:00,125 --> 00:06:02,125
and she's stunningly beautiful,
just like you are.

130
00:06:02,208 --> 00:06:03,333
Oh, stop it.

131
00:06:03,416 --> 00:06:05,000
Ooh, do mine next.
Uh, master.

132
00:06:05,083 --> 00:06:07,916
Could this be any more cliché?
Hey, change schools.

133
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,375
Wait. Hold on a sec.
Chill out.

134
00:06:09,458 --> 00:06:10,916
Why are you upset?
Didn't I tell you...

135
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,416
I was gonna be
transferring to your school?

136
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:14,208
No.

137
00:06:14,291 --> 00:06:16,166
Well, I assumed you'd know
what with you being a psychic.

138
00:06:16,250 --> 00:06:18,000
Wrong.
Oh, I think I get it.

139
00:06:18,083 --> 00:06:19,625
Are you worried I'm gonna
tell people about your powers?

140
00:06:19,708 --> 00:06:21,791
First, quit calling me master.

141
00:06:21,875 --> 00:06:23,500
I won't tell anyone, I swear--

142
00:06:23,583 --> 00:06:24,708
[flushes]

143
00:06:24,791 --> 00:06:26,208
The perfect weapon.

144
00:06:26,291 --> 00:06:28,250
It dissolves in water
so there's no evidence.

145
00:06:28,333 --> 00:06:30,250
[stammers] I feel like a kid

146
00:06:30,333 --> 00:06:32,166
who just got beaten up by the
school bully on his first day.

147
00:06:32,250 --> 00:06:34,125
I don't get why
you'd rather hide your powers.

148
00:06:34,208 --> 00:06:35,875
If you showed off what you do,
you'd get so much attention.

149
00:06:35,958 --> 00:06:37,375
That's exactly why.

150
00:06:37,458 --> 00:06:38,833
Then again,
I guess it's kind of creepy

151
00:06:38,916 --> 00:06:40,666
to know someone's
peeking into your brain.

152
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:42,208
Wait. Hold on. Forget brains.

153
00:06:42,291 --> 00:06:43,916
You can peek at
other body parts, too, right?

154
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,625
Wow, so that means
you can see all the girls naked

155
00:06:45,708 --> 00:06:47,250
any time that you want.
Oh, my God. Ahh.

156
00:06:47,333 --> 00:06:49,625
[giggles]

157
00:06:49,708 --> 00:06:50,708
Ahh...

158
00:06:50,791 --> 00:06:52,791
Yep, another boy
in love with me.

159
00:06:52,875 --> 00:06:54,875
Oh, who is that beautiful angel
who just glided past us?

160
00:06:54,958 --> 00:06:56,583
That's Teruhashi.

161
00:06:56,666 --> 00:06:58,208
She just walked by you
for no reason whatsoever.

162
00:06:58,291 --> 00:06:59,916
