165
00:07:02,625 --> 00:07:03,875
[SAIKI] Please
don't be weird.

166
00:07:03,958 --> 00:07:05,458
Look, there he is.
You can see guardian spirits?

167
00:07:05,541 --> 00:07:06,916
Come read our minds.

168
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:09,625
Well, Saiki, I guess
I can make do with this.

169
00:07:09,708 --> 00:07:12,833
Ladies, I'll get to all of you.
One at a time.

170
00:07:12,916 --> 00:07:14,458
Hey, so what is
a guardian spirit?

171
00:07:14,541 --> 00:07:16,125
Like it sounds.

172
00:07:16,208 --> 00:07:17,916
A spirit that always
watches over and protects you.

173
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,541
Cool. So can you
tell me who mine is?

174
00:07:19,625 --> 00:07:21,083
Your spirit is a samurai

175
00:07:21,166 --> 00:07:23,083
who looks like he can
really keep you safe.

176
00:07:23,166 --> 00:07:24,541
Wow.

177
00:07:24,625 --> 00:07:26,125
